Display = ptr object

Note: This type differs from the original X11 type. It's a pointer to opaque object not an opaque object itself.
GC = ptr object

Screen = ptr object
Information about the screen. The contents of this structure are implementation dependent. A Screen should be treated as opaque by application code.

Format structure; describes ZFormat data the screen will understand.
